      "comment": "COMPLETE STRANGER (7) did some work when racing parked at Menangle last week so wasn't disgraced in finishing midfield. Both career wins have come here, the latest two starts back. Draws for a nice trail so has strong claims. PET RANGER (10) put the writing on the wall with back-to-back placings before she led and fought on to score a dogged win here last time out. No favours expected from this draw but she is going well. JACQUELYN JOY (6) should find this easier than her last attempt at Menangle and finished top-four in her other three starts here after switching from Victoria. CHARLENES DELIGHT (5) drew on the back row and was held up when beaten 6m first up. Improver.",
